<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-3973] Pig CounterColumnFamily support</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-3973</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Included a patch to the current test script to demonstrate that CassandraStorage does not support counter columns, as well as a patch to fix the issue.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The core reason is that CassandraStorage assumes that counters can be unpacked using CounterColumnType, when in fact the column value is already a Long.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;OSX 10.6.latest, Pig 0.9.2&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
